General.Name: Pierce Group AB
General.Description: Pierce Group Ab (publ), an e-commerce company, engages in the sale of motorcycle, gears, parts, and accessories. It operates through Offroad, Onroad, and Other segments. The company serves motocross and enduro riders under the 24MX brand; motorcycle riders on highroads under the XLMOTO brand; and snowmobile riders under the Sledstore brand, as well as through a physical store in Stockholm. Pierce Group Ab (publ) was founded in 2008 and is headquartered in Hägersten, Sweden.
